    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1FeedbackPlugin" kindref="compound">FeedbackPlugin</ref> is an abstract interface, used by Dali-adaptor to access haptic and audio feedback. A concrete implementation must be created for each platform and provided as a dynamic library which will be loaded at run time by the adaptor. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
